    <release version="2.57.0" date="2022-11-16">
      <description>
        <p>What's Changed</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Set window title to "Caprine"</li>
          <li>Completely remove old design code</li>
          <li>Remove new "Install Messenger app" banner</li>
          <li>Fix custom css default file</li>
          <li>Fix search close button color in dark mode</li>
          <li>Fix attachment and receiver pill background in dark mode</li>
          <li>Fix "Join room" background button on dark theme</li>
          <li>Fix create room icon color in dark mode</li>
          <li>Fix dark mode icons</li>
          <li>Fix new room button shortcut</li>
          <li>Fix insert buttons (GIF, Sticker, Emoji, Files) shortcuts</li>
          <li>Fix radio buttons &amp; right sidebar search icon color in dark mode</li>
          <li>Fix new design user menu</li>
          <li>Fix voice message duration text color</li>
        </ul>
      </description>
    </release>
    <release date="2022-08-22" version="2.56.1">
      <description>
        <p>What's New</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Create new room</li>
        </ul>
        <p>What's Changed</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Dark mode fixes (top gap, icons, radio buttons' accent color)</li>
          <li>Fix insert buttons (GIF, Sticker, Emoji, Files)</li>
          <li>Fix "Find Conversation" feature</li>
          <li>Fix "Show Message Buttons" option</li>
          <li>Fix private mode</li>
          <li>Remove code related to old design</li>
          <li>Various improvements to readme</li>
        </ul>
      </description>
    </release>
    <release date="2022-08-17" version="2.56.0">
      <description>
        <ul>
          <li>Update Electron to 20 by @1nikolas, @nehalvpatel and @lefterisgar</li>
          <li>Update to the new Messenger icon (2020)</li>
          <li>Improved scrollbar theme by @mquevill in #1638</li>
          <li>Add dark mode to cookies notification</li>
          <li>Add maintainers in about dialog by @lefterisgar in #1874</li>
          <li>Add option to disable automatic updates</li>
          <li>Enable auto-updates on Linux</li>
          <li>Display a notification when a new update is available</li>
          <li>Fix private mode</li>
          <li>Fix adaptive, hidden and narrow sidebar</li>
          <li>Fix "Show Message Buttons" option</li>
          <li>Fix login button color in dark mode</li>
          <li>Fix cookies notification accept button being hidden on smaller windows</li>
          <li>Fix Caprine not starting on some Linux distros</li>
          <li>Fix ci build step by @dusansimic in #1872</li>
          <li>Fix search icon dark mode color in right sidebar by @dusansimic in #1849</li>
          <li>Fix shortcuts by @dusansimic in #1851</li>
          <li>Hide all non-working features</li>
          <li>Hide new Messenger app banner by @1nikolas in lefterisgar#2</li>
          <li>Select log out as last menu item by @mquevill in #1853</li>
          <li>Remove "Allow All Cookies" button to increase privacy</li>
          <li>Remove all CSS related to old design</li>
        </ul>
      </description>
    </release>
